  <h1>Kids <span>Singing Competition</span></h1>

  <p>
    Rhythm Rise proudly organizes professionally managed kids singing competitions
    to nurture young talent in a positive, encouraging, and safe environment.
    Our platform is designed to help children build confidence, musical skills,
    and stage presence without pressure.
  </p>

  <h2>Age Groups</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>5 – 8 years</li>
    <li>9 – 12 years</li>
    <li>13 – 16 years</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Focus Areas</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Voice clarity and pitch (sur)</li>
    <li>Rhythm and timing</li>
    <li>Expression and confidence</li>
    <li>Age-appropriate song selection</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why Parents Trust Rhythm Rise</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Child-friendly judging system</li>
    <li>Encouraging and constructive feedback</li>
    <li>No favoritism or bias</li>
    <li>Certificates and recognition for all participants</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Languages & Music Styles</h2>
